153
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,000
I know.

154
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:55,040
You’re a good little girl.

155
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,400
However,

156
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:00,200
