165
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:14,200
Mom and Dad will worry about you.

166
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:18,080
I think

167
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:20,660
Haoyue doesn’t want to tell you.

168
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:22,400
Maybe

169
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:25,120
